                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9960" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0627</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2041 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">AI赋能校园招聘：美的集团数字化选才实践</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">AI-Empowered Campus Recruitment: Midea Group&#39;s Digital Talent Selection Practice</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王红丽，代芸，陈政任，姜军辉（通讯作者），周梦楠，刘栋，李振</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华南理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">美的集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家电行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">AI面试；人机协同；数字化人力资源管理；招聘流程重构；2025百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">AI Interview; Human-Machine Collaboration; Digital HR Management; Recruitment Process Redesign</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">美的集团作为中国制造业领军企业，在数字化转型背景下，面对传统招聘效率较低和求职者要求日益增加的双重挑战下，创新性地引入AI重塑招聘流程。本案例详细记录了美的集团人力资源部招聘团队从提案规划到落地实施的全过程：通过引入HRTPS公司的AI面试技术，美的构建定制化胜任力评估模型、建立专属常模，在校园招聘中实现初筛通过率与人类通过率相当。改革过程中，团队采取“试点-反馈-优化”的渐进式流程改造策略。案例深度剖析了制造业龙头如何通过ESIA分析方法实现流程再造、基于信号理论优化候选人体验，并平衡技术效率与伦理责任。揭示数字化转型中“技术赋能管理”的核心逻辑，为中国制造向中国智造转型提供鲜活样本。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a leading enterprise in China&#39;s manufacturing sector, Midea Group has pioneered AI integration to revolutionize its recruitment processes amidst digital transformation, confronting dual pressures of inefficient traditional hiring and escalating candidate expectations. This case study chronicles Midea&#39;s HR team end-to-end journey—from strategic proposal to implementation—detailing how the adoption of HRTPS&#39;s AI interview technology enabled the development of customized competency assessment models and proprietary benchmarks, achieving initial screening pass rates rivaling human evaluators in campus recruitment. Through a phased &quot;pilot-feedback-optimization&quot; approach, the organization exemplifies how manufacturing leaders leverage ESIA methodology for process reengineering, while applying signaling theory to refine candidate experience and maintaining ethical-technology equilibrium. The case ultimately deciphers the &quot;technology-empowered management&quot; paradigm driving digital transformation, serving as a vibrant example of China&#39;s shift from &quot;Made in China&quot; to &quot;Created in China.&quot;</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《招聘与配置》、《组织行为学》、《人工智能赋能人力资源》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">流程再造理论；招聘流程模型；行为面试法；招聘模式比较；KSAM模型；岗位胜任力模型；信号理论；雇主品牌；招聘有效性；招聘漏斗模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-10</td>
                            </tr>
